high_descs: Turn right and again turn right, then go forward to reach near the sink.
Grab the bottle kept near the wall.
Turn around and go forward and after entering the living room, the turn right and go ahead till reaching the far end, then turn right and go near the cabinet.
Keep the bottle in the cabinet under the wash basin.
Turn to left and then turn right.
Grab the similar bottle on the wash basin.
Turn a full circle towards the cabinet.
Keep the bottle in the cabinet under the wash basin.
anns.task_desc: Keep one bottle near the sink and one on the wash basin inside the cabinet under the wash basin.

high_descs: Turn around to walk to the kitchen sink in the front.
Pick up the bottle from the counter to the left of the faucet.
Turn around to walk to the passage, hang right and walk to the bathroom on the right to reach the cabinet under the sink.
Put the bottle in the cabinet.
Look up to face the sink.
Pick up the bottle on top of the sink.
Look down to face the cabinet under the sink.
Put the bottle in the cabinet next to the other bottle.
anns.task_desc: Put two bottles in the cabinet.

high_descs: Turn around and go to towards the sink in the kitchen area.
Pick up the bottle on the right.
Turn around, go ahead and take a right, then right again into the cabinet.
Place the bottle into the cabinet beneath the sink.
Look up to the sink.
Pick up the second bottle on top of the kitchen sink.
Look down towards the cabinet again.
Place the second bottle into the same cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Place two bottles into a bathroom cabinet.
